#. type: Content of: <html><body><h1>
#: fsfe.org/contribute/spreadtheword-freebie.en.xhtml:6
#: fsfe.org/contribute/spreadtheword-freebie.en.xhtml:15
msgid "We offer things for free, but..."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <html><body><p>
#: fsfe.org/contribute/spreadtheword-freebie.en.xhtml:13
#, fuzzy
msgid "<a href=\"/contribute/spreadtheword.html\">Spread the word!</a>"
msgstr "<a href=\"/contribute/spreadtheword.html\">Corre la voz</a>"

#. type: Content of: <html><body><div><p>
#: fsfe.org/contribute/spreadtheword-freebie.en.xhtml:19
msgid ""
"Thank you for your interest in exploring our promotion material.  It seems "
"you visited us via a freebie website offering things you can get for free. "
"We would like to ask you to think about your reasons to order free promotion "
"material from us."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <html><body><p>
#: fsfe.org/contribute/spreadtheword-freebie.en.xhtml:27
msgid ""
"The Free Software Foundation Europe (FSFE) is a non-profit organisation to "
"<a href=\"/about/mission.html\">empower users to control technology</a>. We "
"enjoy giving our volunteers and interested people the possibility to order "
"promotion and information material for free to enable them to fight for <a "
"href=\"/freesoftware\">Free Software</a>."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <html><body><p>
#: fsfe.org/contribute/spreadtheword-freebie.en.xhtml:35
msgid ""
"However, as a charity we cannot afford sending out masses of promotion "
"material for personal use only. We are not making any profit from providing "
"stickers, posters and leaflets. Our strict <a href=\"/about/legal/"
"imprint.html#id-privacy-policy\">privacy policy</a> also disallows abuse of "
"any personal information people provide in the order forms."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <html><body><p>
#: fsfe.org/contribute/spreadtheword-freebie.en.xhtml:43
msgid ""
"Therefore, we would like to ask you to rethink whether you really need such "
"a package. For your decision, please consider the shipping and material "
"costs this causes, as well as the ecological footprint. If you never heard "
"of Free Software and the FSFE before, please learn more about <a href=\"/"
"freesoftware\">Free Software</a>, <a href=\"/about/ourwork.html\">our work</"
"a> and <a href=\"/activities/activities.html\">activities</a> first."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <html><body><p>
#: fsfe.org/contribute/spreadtheword-freebie.en.xhtml:52
msgid ""
"If you feel enthusiastic about our work, we are happy to <a href=\"/"
"promo\">send you information material</a>. Please also have a look at our "
"latest <a href=\"/order\">t-shirts, hoodies and merchandise</a> and consider "
"becoming a <a href=\"https://my.fsfe.org/donate\">supporter or donor of the "
"FSFE</a>. Thank you!"
msgstr ""

